Sentencas: The kinetics of oxygen reduction over various Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3(SSC)-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3(LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 (interlayer)/LSGMC5 (electrolyte) assemblies were studied, which were essential to find the role of an interlayer in improving the performance of an electrode/electrolyte interface.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface

Sentencas: Two major arcs were identified in the impedance spectra at near equilibrium conditions.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface

Sentencas: The reciprocal of the electrode resistance corresponding to the high frequency arc showed a P-O2 dependency about 0.5 at 1073 K and decreased to one-fourth at 873 K, suggesting that the rate-determining step (rds) changed from the dissociative adsorption of oxygen or diffusion of adsorbed oxygen atoms to charge transfer.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface

Sentencas: The reciprocal of the electrode resistance corresponding to the low frequency arc showed a P-O2 dependency about 1, suggesting an rds involving the gas diffusion of oxygen.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface

Sentencas: DC polarization curves of various assemblies agreed well with the Butler-Volmer equation.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface

Sentencas: Both the cathodic and anodic charge transfer coefficients were about 1, and the P-O2 dependencies of the exchange current densities were about 0.25, especially at low temperatures.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface

Sentencas: The characteristics under polarization corresponded to a charge transfer process.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface

Sentencas: The introduction of an LSGMC5 interlayer between the SSC-LSGMC5 electrode and LSGMC5 electrolyte did not change the reaction mechanism, and the role of the interlayer was to increase the number of active sites for oxygen reduction.
Titulo: Kinetic study on the role of an LSGMC5 interlayer in improving the performance of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3 (LSGMC5)/LSGMC5 interface
